e angular KK\nparticles can be weaker than gravitational.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2008 22:44:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jul 2008 18:08:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-12-18"}
