ay gene expression\ndata, are provided to demonstrate the utility and advantage of the proposed\nmethod.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Feb 2008 14:53:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2008 08:07:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-03-26"}
